    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings on the passenger side, and clear coat fading on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and the driver's seat shows significant wear, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car is sound; the engine starts reliably and the brakes are responsive, although it will likely need a suspension tune-up in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any hidden surprises.",
