    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m selling my car and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super dependable for me and still looks great on the road. It has a few little signs of love here and there, but it runs like a charm and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
