    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and style, perfect for a driver who values a well-cared-for machine. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you will find minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather seats are supple and free of tears, showing only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. Every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that pulls cleanly. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, honest vehicle that is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle exemplifies a standard of care that ensures both long-term reliability and significant aesthetic appeal. Meticulously maintained and performance-tested, it offers a sophisticated driving experience tailored for the discerning owner. This offering represents a superior value proposition for those who demand mechanical integrity and a refined presence on the road.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
